## Common Questions & Gotchas

### "Do I need to restart Agent Zero?"

No. Settings are loaded fresh each time an agent with that profile is created.

### "What if I make a mistake in the file?"

If `settings.json` has errors (like a missing comma), the agent will fall back to your default settings. Check that your file is valid JSON if things aren't working.

### "Will this affect my main agent?"

It may do. Your main Agent Zero keeps using whatever you configured in the main settings if no settings.json exists in its profile. You will see "Loaded custom settings for agent 0 with profile 'example_profile' in the UI if it does.

### "What if I don't include a setting?"

Anything you don't specify will use your default settings. You only need to include what you want to *change*.

