## Complete Settings Reference

Below is the **full list** of settings you can override in a profile's `settings.json`. You only need to include the ones you want to change.

### 🤖 Chat Model (Main AI)

The primary model the agent uses for conversations and reasoning.

| Setting | What it does | Example |
|---------|--------------|--------|
| `chat_model_provider` | Which AI company | `"openai"`, `"anthropic"`, `"ollama"` |
| `chat_model_name` | Which specific model | `"gpt-4o"`, `"claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022"` |
| `chat_model_api_base` | Custom API endpoint | `"https://my-server.com/v1"` |
| `chat_model_kwargs` | Extra parameters (see below) | `{"temperature": 0.7}` |
| `chat_model_ctx_length` | Max context window size | `128000` |
| `chat_model_ctx_history` | How much history to keep (0-1) | `0.5` |
| `chat_model_vision` | Enable image understanding | `true` or `false` |
| `chat_model_rl_requests` | Rate limit: requests/min | `60` |
| `chat_model_rl_input` | Rate limit: input tokens/min | `100000` |
| `chat_model_rl_output` | Rate limit: output tokens/min | `50000` |

### 🔧 Utility Model

A secondary model for background tasks like summarization.

| Setting | What it does | Example |
|---------|--------------|--------|
| `util_model_provider` | Which AI company | `"openai"` |
| `util_model_name` | Which specific model | `"gpt-4o-mini"` |
| `util_model_api_base` | Custom API endpoint | `"https://my-server.com/v1"` |
| `util_model_kwargs` | Extra parameters | `{"temperature": 0.3}` |
| `util_model_ctx_length` | Max context window size | `16000` |
| `util_model_ctx_input` | Max input ratio (0-1) | `0.8` |
| `util_model_rl_requests` | Rate limit: requests/min | `100` |
| `util_model_rl_input` | Rate limit: input tokens/min | `200000` |
| `util_model_rl_output` | Rate limit: output tokens/min | `100000` |

### 🌐 Browser Model

Used when the agent controls a web browser.

| Setting | What it does | Example |
|---------|--------------|--------|
| `browser_model_provider` | Which AI company | `"openai"` |
| `browser_model_name` | Which specific model | `"gpt-4o"` |
| `browser_model_api_base` | Custom API endpoint | `"https://my-server.com/v1"` |
| `browser_model_kwargs` | Extra parameters | `{"temperature": 0.2}` |
| `browser_model_vision` | Enable screenshot analysis | `true` |
| `browser_model_rl_requests` | Rate limit: requests/min | `30` |
| `browser_model_rl_input` | Rate limit: input tokens/min | `50000` |
| `browser_model_rl_output` | Rate limit: output tokens/min | `25000` |
| `browser_http_headers` | Custom HTTP headers | `{"User-Agent": "..."}` |

### 📁 Agent Identity & Storage

| Setting | What it does | Example |
|---------|--------------|--------|
| `agent_profile` | Default profile to use | `"researcher"` |
| `agent_memory_subdir` | Memory storage folder | `"legal_team"` |
| `agent_knowledge_subdir` | Knowledge import folder | `"legal_docs"` |

### 🧠 Memory & Recall

Controls how the agent remembers and retrieves information.

| Setting | What it does | Example |
|---------|--------------|--------|
| `memory_recall_enabled` | Enable memory search | `true` |
| `memory_recall_delayed` | Delay recall for batching | `false` |
| `memory_recall_interval` | Recall check interval (msgs) | `3` |
| `memory_recall_history_len` | Messages to consider | `5` |
| `memory_recall_memories_max_search` | Max memories to search | `100` |
| `memory_recall_solutions_max_search` | Max solutions to search | `50` |
| `memory_recall_memories_max_result` | Max memories returned | `5` |
| `memory_recall_solutions_max_result` | Max solutions returned | `3` |
| `memory_recall_similarity_threshold` | Match strictness (0-1) | `0.7` |
| `memory_recall_query_prep` | Preprocess search queries | `true` |
| `memory_recall_post_filter` | Filter results after search | `true` |
| `memory_memorize_enabled` | Enable saving memories | `true` |
| `memory_memorize_consolidation` | Merge similar memories | `true` |
| `memory_memorize_replace_threshold` | Similarity to replace (0-1) | `0.9` |

