## Quick Reference

### Minimal settings.json
```json
{
  "chat_model_provider": "openai",
  "chat_model_name": "gpt-4o-mini"
}
```

### With temperature adjustment
```json
{
  "chat_model_provider": "anthropic",
  "chat_model_name": "claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022",
  "chat_model_kwargs": {
    "temperature": 0.2
  }
}
```

### With custom knowledge folder
```json
{
  "chat_model_provider": "openai",
  "chat_model_name": "gpt-4o",
  "agent_knowledge_subdir": "legal_docs",
  "agent_memory_subdir": "legal_team"
}
```

### Full example (all model types)
```json
{
  "chat_model_provider": "anthropic",
  "chat_model_name": "claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022",
  "chat_model_kwargs": { "temperature": 0.3 },
  
  "util_model_provider": "openai",
  "util_model_name": "gpt-4o-mini",
  
  "agent_knowledge_subdir": "research",
  "memory_recall_similarity_threshold": 0.6
}
```

### Profile folder structure
```
/a0/agents/your_profile/
├── _context.md        ← Description (recommended)
├── settings.json      ← Model settings (this feature)
└── prompts/           ← Custom instructions (optional)
    └── agent.system.main.role.md
```

